      "description": "Offered is an exceptional FD3S chassis featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary powerplant. This specimen retains its complex sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering a linear power band with no boost leaks or actuator hesitation. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Suspension kinematics remain factory-true with a double-wishbone setup and zero bushing deflection. Meticulously maintained with a focus on thermal management and vacuum system integrity, this RX-7 represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering in showroom-caliber condition.",
